    public abstract class AbstractObject
extends java.lang.Object
    The AbstractObject is the core class of SBML2Modelica. It is the main component of an AbstractModel, because every element of the latter is an AbstractObject. An AbstractObject is uniquely identified by a String identifier, and also it could have an optional name. Note that an AbstractObject MUST have an identifier and two AbstractObjects with the same identifier are considered equals.
